Link in bio @drjoedispenza⁣ 👈⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Continue reading to learn more👇⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
Imagine if you could heal and create the future of your dreams all at the same time? Dr. Joe is demystifying the process of change and doing what seems like very supernatural things in science/medical community. People are healing from all types of diseases and cancer using his formula for change. But not only that, he teaches you how to manifest using quantum physics to live the life of your dreams.⁣ All while being backed by science! 🧬⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
"The latest research on epigenetics tells us that the environment signals the gene, and the end product from an experience in the environment is an emotion, as we embrace the emotion ahead of the environment, we are signaling the gene ahead of the environment." - Dr. Joe Dispenza ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
Click the link in @drjoedispenza bio to be apart of his upcoming live stream where he will share this formula!🦋

node.text:
Follow ➡️ @flippin_az 💣
 FlipFam 🚀🎯 🙌
Day in The Life of AIrbnb Journey 💰🔐

Welcome- Courtney @clmpilates and Facebook page CLM Pilates to the team. 💪💪

Courtney grew up in small town upper state New York.

What she brings to our Airbnb team- values, efficiency, hard work, and get shit done attitude.

One of the best things my mentor taught me was having fun building a business and make money 💰 at same time.

What is better in life?!
As you know FlipNation our journey/goal for 2021 is 10 properties- we should be completed with 5 by my bday in April🎯🎯🎯

I remind myself daily the following:

1. This could be last day so make sure you put 110 percent in family, friends, and biz- most importantly find joy in you. ❤️
2. Hang out with extraordinary people if you want to do extraordinary things- we ain’t got time for ordinary
3. Drama is a no go in life and biz cut the drama seekers off at the path.
4. Two way street- make sure you surround yourself with folks who got your back
Takers are all around but you only want the people around who make you better
5. Give it all you got- don’t slow down because it’s not really about you- get rid of ego
6. Service is the key 🔐 
7. Failure is nothing but feedback, I can’t tell you guys how many times I have failed and I am sure more failure is coming- making me strong 💪 I welcome it and attack it
8. Face the problems and figure out solutions asap
9. Communication 
10. Most importantly live your dream 😴 and no one else’s- Do you and do you to best of your ability- Do good for others ❤️❤️

FlipFam-stay tuned to more on the AirBNB vision plan as I document our journey 🎯✍️

If you want to make 2021 your best year ever, then read this short caption for 1 minute... ⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣

Most people follow the crowd and expect to be successful and unique. ⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
